      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_1838274773517086661.png",
                "id": "talent14433",
                "key": "Frostblade Hailstorm",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Frostblade Hailstorm"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span>. The target character receives <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Sheer Cold</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Sheer Cold</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">End Phase:</span> Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span> to attached character.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 1</span><br><br>When attached character has <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Blazing Heat</span> attached, remove this effect.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/289913e1d0feaab0fa03891032b086c0_6564273064286193397.png",
                "id": "talent25734",
                "key": "Biting Shards",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Biting Shards"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, heals this character for 2 HP. Removes <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Ice-Sealed Crimson Witch of Embers</span>. This character permanently switches to <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Crimson Witch of Embers</span> state.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Ice-Sealed Crimson Witch of Embers</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the Action Phase starts:</span> If the attached character has no more than 4 HP, remove this effect.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When attached character is defeated:</span> Remove this effect, ensure that character <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">will not be defeated</span> and heal them to 1 HP.<br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When this effect is removed:</span> Attached character will transform into the <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Crimson Witch of Embers</span> state.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Immunity to Defeat</span></strong></p><p>Certain effects will grant characters an<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> immunity to being defeated</span> when their HP hits 0, and will heal them for a certain amount thereafter.</p><p>When this occurs, characters will not be regarded as having experienced a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">defeat</span>. (Hence, their attached equipment and statuses will not be removed, and their Energy will remain uncleared.)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Crimson Witch of Embers</span></strong><br>La Signora can permanently change into the \"Crimson Witch of Embers\" state.<br>After changing, La Signora's Elemental Type changes from <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo </span>to <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro</span>.<br>After changing, this character can use the skills of the Crimson Witch of Embers, but can no longer use La Signora's original skills.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/f819c287507962ff41ad86e68661a707_947775150484171905.png",
                "id": "talent57166",
                "key": "Carmine Chrysalis",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Carmine Chrysalis"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive) When the battle begins, this character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Ice-Sealed Crimson Witch of Embers</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Ice-Sealed Crimson Witch of Embers</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the Action Phase starts:</span> If the attached character has no more than 4 HP, remove this effect.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When attached character is defeated:</span> Remove this effect, ensure that character and heal them to 1 HP.<br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When this effect is removed:</span> Attached character will transform into the <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Crimson Witch of Embers</span> state.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Immunity to Defeat</span></strong></p><p>Certain effects will grant characters an<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> immunity to being defeated</span> when their HP hits 0, and will heal them for a certain amount thereafter.</p><p>When this occurs, characters will not be regarded as having experienced a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">defeat</span>. (Hence, their attached equipment and statuses will not be removed, and their Energy will remain uncleared.)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Crimson Witch of Embers</span></strong><br>Signora can permanently change into the \"Crimson Witch of Embers\" state.<br>After changing, Signora's Elemental Type changes from <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>to <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>.<br>After changing, this character can use the skills of the Crimson Witch of Embers, but can no longer use Signora's original skills.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/fd49675d27422f60ca4f0227ea422dec_3138177847449158687.png",
                "id": "talent73687",
                "key": "Might of Delusion",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Might of Delusion"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_3098711621446450601.png",
