              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro DMG</span>. The target character received <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Blazing Heat</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Blazing Heat</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro DMG</span> to attached character.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span><br><br>When attached character has <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Sheer Cold </span>attached, remove this effect.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/9893e5160645321019bda81ec8ac1125_6674133087434803788.png",
